### Is

~~~ .php.xmp
Request::is($id = null, $key = null);
~~~

**Example:**

~~~ .php
if (Request::is('post')) {
    // Is a `POST` request!
}
~~~

~~~ .php
if (Request::is('post', 'time')) {
    // Is has `time` key in `$_POST` array either it contains a value or not
    // This is equal to `if (array_key_exists('time', $_POST ?? [])) {}`
}

if (Request::post('time')) {
    // Is has `time` key in `$_POST` array and it contains a value
    // This is equal to `if (!empty($_POST['time'])) {}`
}
~~~